OL,5, As temperatures rise, prisoners locked 
OL,6, in cells without air conditioning - and
OL,7, the staff guarding them - are          
OL,8, struggling.                            
OL,10,FCalvin Johnson spent 37 years in a     
OL,11,FTexas state prison, including 37       
OL,12,Fsummers in a jail cell with no air     
OL,13,Fconditioning.                          
OL,15,FOn the countless blisteringly hot days,
OL,16,Fwhen temperatures climbed above 37.7C  
OL,17,F(100F), his survival depended upon a   
OL,18,Fmix of creativity and desperation to   
OL,19,Fstay cool - stay alive.                
